    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "support groups don't really fix the fact that i'm losing myself. every day i feel less like a person and more like a patient. it's like i'm just stuck in this waiting room for death, watching my life slip away through a crack in the door. i just wish i could have some kind of agency in all this... to have a say in how this chapter ends instead of just being dragged along by this pain.",
